This page was written as a stop-gap while <nowiki>[[http://cloud-images.ubuntu.com|cloud-images.ubuntu.com]]</nowiki> was updated. All supported AMI's in all current EC2 regions can be found at <nowiki>[[http://cloud-images.ubuntu.com|cloud-images.ubuntu.com]]</nowiki>.

== US-West-2 AMI's ==

On 2011-11-08 at 22:00 PDT, Amazon Launched the brand new US-West-2 Zone located in Oregon. 

Canonical is pleased to announce that all supported Ubuntu images are currently available in US-West-2 at launch. On 2011-11-09, daily builds will start appearing in the new region.
